# 1. Ignore Python system cache files
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# 2. Ignore Jupyter Notebook temporary checkpoints
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# 3. Ignore any exported audio files you generate during testing
*.mp3

# 4. Ignore all general text files by default to keep the repo clean
*.txt

# 5. EXCEPTION: Explicitly allow Git to see your example story folder and file
!Short stories/
!Short stories/A small bird.txt